caffsim
  • Reference

Create a dataset for simulation of multiple dose of caffeine

DatasetMulti will create a dataset for simulation of multiple dose of caffeine

DatasetMulti(Weight, Dose, N = 20, Tau = 24)

Arguments

Weight

Body weight (kg)
Dose

Dose of multiple caffeine (mg)
N

The number of simulated subjects
Tau

The interval of multiple dosing (hour)

Value

The dataset of pharmacokinetic parameters of subjects after multiple caffeine dose following multivariate normal

See also

http://asancpt.github.io/CaffeineEdison

Examples

DatasetMulti(Weight = 20, Dose = 200, N = 20, Tau = 8)
